{"bgColorIndex":0,"note":"Add legal email billing heuristics:\n\n- If a reply is sent, create a default 0.1 suggested entry unless stronger evidence supports more time.\n- If multiple replies occur in one thread within 30 minutes, cluster them and suggest 0.2 or 0.3.\n- If a reply includes an attachment or follows a document-open event, increase confidence and suggested time.\n- If other events exist between email received and reply sent, do not bill the full gap automatically.\n- Match email events to cases using contact email, thread metadata, and subject line.\n- Create a clean utility module for these heuristics and add testable helper functions.","textColorIndex":0}